  "body": "In order to enable the LES protocol by default in the future, we still have a few things need to be fixed\r\n\r\n* [x] Now the LES-server is not allowed to un-index the transactions #21909\r\n* [ ] ~If the eth protocol slot is full, then all the real tcp connection will be dropped in order to fill the les slots~\r\n* [x] Enable the discv5 for LES #21940\r\n* [x] Enable hive rpc test for light client  https://github.com/ethereum/hive/pull/424 https://github.com/ethereum/hive/pull/432\r\n* [x] Fuzz the LES protocol(especially the server-handler)\r\n* [x] Fuzz node state machine #21970\r\n* [x] Add the forkID to the LES4 #21907\r\n* [ ] standardize the beacon-node API to provide ETH2.0 light client data\r\n* [ ] Expose the LES4 protocol to public\r\n",
